sect2.para:
Note that @size directive must be included in the product definition files BEFORE any directives which display data!


&dircols;
&keyhead;





columns

integer

Number of columns (characters) in output file




rows

integer

Number of rows (lines) in output file





@size { width = 80; height = 120; }
Set the size of the ASCII output file to 80 columns (characters) by 120 rows (lines).
